# Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock is tracked: this is a binary crate, and the lock pins the reth/alloy
# git-dependency versions (reth v2.3.0 needs the alloy 2.x family held at 2.0.5).
# Without it, a fresh checkout re-resolves and fails to build.

